tuesday in my opinion thats age discrimination of the worst 
sort 
it is time that this depressionera fossil was done away 
with said rep dennis hastert rill chief house sponsor of 
the bill 
hastert said 181 of the 435 house members have signed on as 
cosponsors as have 18 of the 100 senators a big reduction in the 
earnings limit was approved by the full house and by the senate 
finance committee last year but died in the senate as part of a 
deficitreduction agreement 
democratic leaders have fought the repeal bill over the years 
for two reasons 
they note the first limit was placed in the law in 1939 even 
before the first social security check was ever written to ensure 
