development officials said hud had received an identical request 
coleman later confirmed sending the letters to all the major 
government departments and independent agencies 
the ethics committee is conducting a preliminary inquiry to 
determine whether it should begin a triallike investigation of a 
series of allegations made against damato by mark green his 
democratic election opponent in 1986 
green filed the complaint after numerous news accounts detailed 
the senators successful lobbying of hud officials for housing and 
other developments in new york and puerto rico including a 
