openended request for copies of foia responses and if it decided 
to comply whether hud should identify the reporter or organization 
requesting the information 
the hud official speaking on the condition of anonymity said 
that if the department complied with the request it could receive 
similar letters from other members of congress reporters and 
others opening the door for a paperwork nightmare 
