announces the following 
first during the prolonged american darkness that has engulfed 
the region all have fallen into us traps intentions are 
obscured guns have been deviated and rules of classifying friends 
and foes by members of the same ranks have changed painful stabs 
have been dealt to our essential causes strugglers and martyrs 
have fallen in the arenas of shame everywhere with america behind 
them above them and in between them not to say inside of them all 
in this deluge and in spite of all the revolutionary justice 
organization remains and remains and remains holding to its 
positions and directing all its efforts and strugglers against 
america and its allies only america and its allies the 
organization counsels all that this is the right and sole course to 
which suicide strugglers and special operations should be directed 
they should wake up and ponder what they do 
