the universitys freshman class of about 800 students was sent 
to an academy in hebei south of the capital for training that the 
official press said included firing guns and throwing grenades 
beijing university played a major role last spring in the 
studentled prodemocracy movement which was crushed by the 
military and the school was singled out by the government as it 
acted to prevent a repeat of the movement 
on wednesday teng teng vice chairman of the state education 
commission said of the military training program if the 
experiment works out we can apply it to other institutions 
teng spoke with reporters at jomtien near bangkok where he was 
attending an international conference on education 
