university students who participated also worked in factories and 
on farms the aim was to bring students into contact with soldiers 
workers and farmers to let them know what the realities are 
teng said 
he said the program has had mixed results 
some of the effect is sound and some not so favorable teng 
said without elaborating 
but he added it has greatly enhanced discipline among 
students 
