1987 the day poindexter began giving testimony to congress on 
national television under a grant of immunity from prosecution 
north has said he is unable to differentiate what he knows from 
poindexters immunized testimony and what he knows from his own 
experiences in the irancontra affair under federal law no part 
of the prosecutions case may be derived from a defendants 
immunized testimony 
