will come back to them 
perriers davis said consumer surveys the company has taken 
indicate 95 percent of perrier users feel the company acted 
responsibly in ordering the recall and 84 percent plan to purchase 
it in the future 
he said he could not estimate the costs of the recall in the 
united states 
but he said the perrier brand would have sold about 30 million 
in the months that it will be off the shelf or in limited supply 
offsetting that however would be gains in sales of perrier 
groups other brands including arrowhead poland spring and 
calistoga 
davis said at least 50 percent of perrier brands shelf space in 
