leaves office july 28 accumulated inflation during his fiveyear 
term will reach 1383120 percent 
novelist mario vargas llosa is favored to win the april 8 
presidential election as the candidate of a centerright coalition 
he has pledged to reduce annual inflation to 10 percent within a 
year but says it will demand great sacrifice 
after five years of garcia who campaigned as the president of 
hope and won by a landslide many peruvians are skeptical of 
politicians promises 
all thats left to believe in is ourselves miss mandujano 
said 
