amendments 
senate majority leader george mitchell dmaine complained that 
senators were slow in producing amendments and vowed to keep the 
legislation on the floor until we see some progress even if it 
means working into the weekend 
we cant permit legislation of this magnitude not to proceed 
because no senator wants to come forward with an amendment 
mitchell declared in an almost empty senate chamber late tuesday 
despite the lack of floor action there was considerable 
