options pratt would supply an additional 135 engines including 
spares worth nearly 13 billion 
deliveries will begin in 1994 and carry through the end of the 
decade long said 
to put the magnitude of the order in perspective all airline 
orders for pratts popular pw4000 engine in 1989 combined totalled 
700 engines worth about 47 billion long said 
selwyn berson president of pratts commercial engine business 
said he was pleased that singapore which has an exclusively 
prattpowered fleet of aircraft intends to continue its 
relationship with the jetengine maker 
in a prepared statement on the orders singapore airlines said 
the decision to remain with pratt engines came after four months 
of exhaustive evaluation 
the company said it also had considered engines produced by 
pratts major rivals general electrics cf680c2 and 
rollsroyces trent 650 but concluded that while all three 
companies offered highquality hightechnology products pratts 
engines were preferable 
taking into account all factors including financial and 
technical sia decided that pratt amp whitney engines had the 
edge over the other engines the airlines statement said 
airline officials also said the new aircraft will permit the 
company to compete better and take advantage of growth 
opportunities provided by the changing global environment 
in addition to providing modern power the airline said the new 
prattpowered fleet will be more fuel efficient and help reduce 
pollution as well as costs 
