will result in about 2200 workers being laid off was scheduled 
for midmarch now gm says it wont happen until april or may 
chrysler also indefinitely suspended some planned reductions in 
assembly line speeds which also would have resulted in indefinite 
layoffs ford plans no changes in production that will result in 
layoffs 
